a Kofun|ja|今宿大塚古墳}} - Located in {{ill|Nishi-ku, Fukuoka|ja|福岡市西区}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Imajuku Kofun Cluster|ja|今宿古墳群}}. Designated a national historic site. * {{ill|Tanushimaru Ōtsuka Kofun|ja|田主丸大塚古墳}} - Located in {{ill|Tanushimaru, Fukuoka|ja|浮羽郡田主丸町}}, Fukuoka Prefecture. Part of the {{ill|Tanushimaru Kofun Cluster|ja|田主丸古墳群}}. Designated a national historic site.
